Hope you'll like it, recipe bellow ---- ğŸ¥§ For the shortcrust pastry: 250 g of flour, 125 g of caster sugar, 1 egg, 100 g of butter, 1 lemon zest, 1 pinch of salt  In a bowl, mix the egg with powdered sugar and a pinch of salt.  Put the flour on the worktop, make a well in the center, pour the contents of the bowl and the lemon zest, then the melted butter (especially not liquid butter!). Mix everything until you get a homogeneous paste. Roll it out.  Bake in a hot oven for 12 to 15 minutes.
